@startuml poster_skills_heritage
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam titleFontSize 20
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

title Lifetime Map: Life Skills & Heritage (0–35)

package "Life Skills" {
  [**0–5 Foundation**\nSelf-care basics\nRoutines] as k1
  [**6–12 Exploration**\nCooking basics\nCleaning\nOrganization] as k2
  [**13–17 Formation**\nLaundry & repairs\nDriving & first aid\nCybersecurity\nAI literacy] as k3
  [**18–24 Launch**\nTaxes & insurance\nBudget & credit\nEmergency prep\nLease/rent] as k4
  [**25–35 Stewardship**\nHome ownership\nLegal literacy\nEstate planning\nCommunity leadership] as k5

  k1 -right-> k2
  k2 -right-> k3
  k3 -right-> k4
  k4 -right-> k5
}

package "Heritage & Identity" {
  [**0–5 Foundation**\nFamily stories\nWhere did\nGrandma live?] as h1
  [**6–12 Exploration**\nFamily tree\nMigration map\nLanguage fragments\nArtifacts preserved] as h2
  [**13–17 Formation**\nAncestor research\nFaith heritage\nOccupation patterns\nHealth awareness] as h3
  [**18–24 Launch**\nHistorical context\nCultural inheritance\nLessons from ancestors\nWhat to keep/end] as h4
  [**25–35 Stewardship**\nResponsibility accepted\nActive preservation\nLegacy creation\nStory transmission] as h5

  h1 -right-> h2
  h2 -right-> h3
  h3 -right-> h4
  h4 -right-> h5
}

note bottom
  Most people inherit money. Very few inherit a map.
  By age 35: 35 years of family, financial, educational, and spiritual history.
end note

@enduml
